<c.bg_transparent>Pero, a veces, las amenazas leves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>son peores que las fuertes.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:13.534 --> 00:08:17.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una palabra dulce puede ser más peligrosa</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que una daga escondida.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:18.289 --> 00:08:22.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mi hijo de 19 años no conoce</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>la mitad de las palabras que dijo.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:22.585 --> 00:08:25.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y aún se niega a comer verduras.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:27.048 --> 00:08:31.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reina Aanya,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿puedo compartirle una historia?</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:31.511 --> 00:08:35.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una historia sobre la época</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>en que los reinos trabajaron juntos</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:35.681 --> 00:08:38.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>para lograr algo milagroso.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:42.188 --> 00:08:46.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hace nueve años,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mi viejo amigo, el príncipe Harrow,</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:46.943 --> 00:08:49.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>se convirtió en el rey de Katolis.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:52.031 --> 00:08:55.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Recuerdo la coronación</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>como si hubiese sido ayer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

118
00:09:17.306 --> 00:09:19.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero marcar una diferencia, Sarai.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:20.142 --> 00:09:23.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo harás.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Serás el campeón del amor y la justicia.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:23.896 --> 00:09:25.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y yo lucharé a tu lado.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:41.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Era un rey hermoso</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>con una familia hermosa,</i></c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:42.123 --> 00:09:44.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>y había esperanza en Katolis.</i></c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:48.212 --> 00:09:49.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ya terminamos?</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:50.423 --> 00:09:51.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece terminado.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:52.758 --> 00:09:55.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, es un retrato excelente, muy bello.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:56.262 --> 00:09:57.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya pueden moverse.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:10:00.141 --> 00:10:02.435 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera. Aún no eres libre.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:10:02.518 --> 00:10:04.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El rey debe posar para uno más.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:10:06.355 --> 00:10:10.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mi retrato oficial.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Para los libros de historia y demás.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:10:15.031 --> 00:10:16.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bien, ¿listo?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:10:16.282 --> 00:10:17.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pon tu mejor cara.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:20.328 --> 00:10:21.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Posa conmigo, Viren.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:22.246 --> 00:10:25.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero es tu retrato oficial como rey.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:25.875 --> 00:10:28.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí. Y tú deberías estar a mi lado.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:29.045 --> 00:10:31.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como sé que lo estarás siempre.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:48.481 --> 00:10:50.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te traje una sorpresa.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:52.276 --> 00:10:53.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tartas de jalea en la cama?</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:54.028 --> 00:10:57.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Podemos hacer lo que queramos,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>somos los reyes.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:11:04.038 --> 00:11:06.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alguien heredó tu gusto por lo dulce.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:14.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ezran es afortunado.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:11:14.465 --> 00:11:16.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nació siendo príncipe, como yo.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:11:17.259 --> 00:11:20.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>En nuestro reino,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>muchos nacieron con menos.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:11:20.221 --> 00:11:22.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué te preocupa, Harrow?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:11:22.890 --> 00:11:24.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué me lo merezco?</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:11:24.934 --> 00:11:28.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué hice,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>además de haber nacido con todo?</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:11:28.813 --> 00:11:32.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres humilde, agradecido y amable.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:11:34.610 --> 00:11:37.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mi padre me dijo que,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por sobre todas las cosas,</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:11:37.822 --> 00:11:39.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>debo ser un rey justo.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:40.241 --> 00:11:43.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando murió,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>soñé con la Dama de la Justicia.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:43.452 --> 00:11:46.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿La Dama de la Justicia?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Estaba vestida.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:48.082 --> 00:11:49.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Qué sueño aburrido.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:49.667 --> 00:11:51.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Puedo seguir?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Claro.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:51.919 --> 00:11:56.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me dijo que la justicia era más</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que decisiones y consecuencias justas.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:56.841 --> 00:12:00.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un sistema justo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>constituye la verdadera justicia.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:12:00.845 --> 00:12:05.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me mostró la balanza,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>la espada y la venda,</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:12:06.142 --> 00:12:07.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y me dijo que eligiera.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:12:07.601 --> 00:12:09.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Elegiste la venda.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:12:09.937 --> 00:12:11.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:12:11.147 --> 00:12:14.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dijo que la venda nos deja</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>probar el sistema.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:12:14.650 --> 00:12:18.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y que debía usarla para imaginarme</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que no había nacido</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:12:18.195 --> 00:12:21.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y que no sabía aún si sería rico o pobre,</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:12:21.782 --> 00:12:23.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ni el color de mi piel,</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:12:23.659 --> 00:12:26.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ni la cultura y las costumbres</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de mi familia.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:12:27.329 --> 00:12:31.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que a un sistema justo no le importan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>las circunstancias de mi nacimiento.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:31.834 --> 00:12:35.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que los derechos, las leyes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y las oportunidades del sistema</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:35.129 --> 00:12:38.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>deberían proteger a todos.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:38.674 --> 00:12:40.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una mujer sabia.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:40.968 --> 00:12:44.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Sí.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Y no se te insinuó?</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:45.014 --> 00:12:46.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sabía que no le convenía.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:48.184 --> 00:12:53.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres muy inspirador cuando dices cosas así</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con jalea en la nariz.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:53.564 --> 00:12:54.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:13:12.416 --> 00:13:14.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>El rey Harrow trabajaba sin cesar.</i></c.bg_transparent>

173
00:13:14.919 --> 00:13:19.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Se consideraba un servidor</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>del pueblo de Katolis,</i></c.bg_transparent>

174
00:13:19.632 --> 00:13:21.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¡un rey servidor!</i></c.bg_transparent>

175
00:13:25.137 --> 00:13:28.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Un día, llegaron dos visitantes de lejos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

176
00:13:28.974 --> 00:13:30.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Desde otro reino.</i></c.bg_transparent>

177
00:13:31.143 --> 00:13:33.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Necesitaban su ayuda desesperadamente.</i></c.bg_transparent>

178
00:13:34.188 --> 00:13:37.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>¿Sabe quiénes eran estas visitantes?</i></c.bg_transparent>

179
00:13:38.818 --> 00:13:40.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mis madres.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:13:40.945 --> 00:13:41.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:14:36.208 --> 00:14:39.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿No se puede tener</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un poco de privacidad?</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:14:40.379 --> 00:14:42.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En serio, déjame en paz.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:14:50.222 --> 00:14:51.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, espera.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:14:52.016 --> 00:14:54.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ven aquí. Me vendría bien la luz.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:14:59.648 --> 00:15:04.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sus madres, las reinas de Duren,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>actuaban con mucha dignidad,</i></c.bg_transparent>

186
00:15:05.446 --> 00:15:07.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>pero había dolor en su mirada.</i></c.bg_transparent>

187
00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:10.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No necesitan arrodillarse.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:15:11.076 --> 00:15:14.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Venimos a rogarle que nos ayude.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:15:14.371 --> 00:15:17.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>El reino de Duren sufre</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una hambruna terrible</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:15:17.541 --> 00:15:19.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>desde hace siete años.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:15:19.335 --> 00:15:21.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya casi no tenemos recursos ni alimento.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:15:22.588 --> 00:15:25.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Este invierno, se acabará la comida</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:15:26.425 --> 00:15:28.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y 100 000 personas morirán.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:15:32.222 --> 00:15:33.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los ayudaremos.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:15:33.766 --> 00:15:37.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Katolis compartirá todo lo que tiene</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con Duren.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:15:43.776 --> 00:15:46.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Querido rey, hablaste demasiado pronto.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:15:47.071 --> 00:15:51.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Katolis apenas le alcanza la comida</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para sobrevivir el invierno.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:15:51.700 --> 00:15:54.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No podemos compartir ni un grano.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:15:55.996 --> 00:15:58.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No les daré la espalda.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:15:58.374 --> 00:16:02.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si compartes con ellos,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>igual morirán 100 000 personas,</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:16:02.836 --> 00:16:05.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero la mitad serán de nuestro reino.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:16:07.341 --> 00:16:09.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No tenemos alternativa.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:16:09.760 --> 00:16:10.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exacto.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:16:11.011 --> 00:16:13.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo comprenderán.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:16:13.931 --> 00:16:16.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Compartiremos lo que haya.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:16:17.059 --> 00:16:19.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y compartiremos su sufrimiento.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:16:27.027 --> 00:16:29.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Harrow ayudaría</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>más allá de las posibilidades.</i></c.bg_transparent>

208
00:16:31.448 --> 00:16:33.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ese invierno, habría hambre y muerte.</i></c.bg_transparent>

209
00:16:34.493 --> 00:16:36.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Una tragedia devastadora...</i></c.bg_transparent>

210
00:16:37.913 --> 00:16:39.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>...era inevitable.</i></c.bg_transparent>

211
00:16:41.417 --> 00:16:45.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pero se me presentó una posibilidad nueva.</i></c.bg_transparent>

212
00:16:45.671 --> 00:16:48.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Estuve investigando.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Ya veo.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:16:51.260 --> 00:16:54.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leí textos antiguos, mapas y archivos.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:16:54.430 --> 00:16:58.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y creo que encontré una solución creativa.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:16:58.851 --> 00:17:01.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Algo que podría salvar vidas.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:17:01.186 --> 00:17:02.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuéntame.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:17:02.521 --> 00:17:03.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Contémplala!</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:17:05.024 --> 00:17:06.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una roca.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:17:06.483 --> 00:17:10.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esta roca es una reliquia de Xadia.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:17:10.696 --> 00:17:15.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es parte de un gran monstruo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un gigante que vive en las montañas:</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:17:15.534 --> 00:17:17.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡un titán de magma!</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:17:19.329 --> 00:17:21.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Está cálida.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Sí.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:17:21.623 --> 00:17:24.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>El titán vive cerca</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de la frontera de Xadia.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:17:24.293 --> 00:17:26.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si lo cazamos y lo matamos,</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:17:27.504 --> 00:17:29.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>puedo usar su corazón</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:17:29.590 --> 00:17:32.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>en un hechizo que calentará la tierra</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:17:32.301 --> 00:17:35.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y podremos cultivar en abundancia.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:17:35.637 --> 00:17:38.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Alcanzará para dos reinos?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Alcanzará para diez!</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:17:40.434 --> 00:17:42.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>En ese entonces,</i></c.bg_transparent>

230
00:17:42.186 --> 00:17:45.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>yo no era el consejero más cercano al rey.</i></c.bg_transparent>

231
00:17:51.528 --> 00:17:53.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Es un error, Harrow!</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:17:53.322 --> 00:17:55.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué te molesta tanto?</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:18:03.165 --> 00:18:06.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Matamos un monstruo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para salvar a miles de personas.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:18:06.335 --> 00:18:08.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo llames monstruo.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:18:08.504 --> 00:18:12.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una bestia de roca y magma.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>O sea, es un monstruo.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:18:19.556 --> 00:18:21.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Es inteligente?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:18:21.934 --> 00:18:23.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué quieres decir?</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:18:23.268 --> 00:18:24.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Piensa? ¿Siente?</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:18:25.646 --> 00:18:26.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tiene familia?</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:18:29.066 --> 00:18:31.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dudo que tenga familia.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:18:31.527 --> 00:18:33.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Es el último de su especie?</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:18:33.862 --> 00:18:35.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Eso qué importa?</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:18:37.783 --> 00:18:40.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece que resolverá todo,</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:18:40.202 --> 00:18:42.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero ¿no es demasiado fácil?</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:18:42.704 --> 00:18:44.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así es la magia oscura.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:18:44.998 --> 00:18:46.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué alternativa tenemos?</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:18:52.381 --> 00:18:54.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quieres mejorar el mundo,</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:56.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>cambiar las cosas.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:18:56.260 --> 00:18:58.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se necesitarán décadas de trabajo duro.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:18:58.762 --> 00:19:02.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ningún monstruo que mates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>resolverá todos tus problemas.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:19:02.349 --> 00:19:03.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No hay camino fácil!</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:19:05.394 --> 00:19:08.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Será una situación resbaladiza.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:19:10.649 --> 00:19:13.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Harrow, dime que no lo harás.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:19:15.112 --> 00:19:17.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es nuestra única posibilidad.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:19:28.167 --> 00:19:30.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entraremos a Xadia por la brecha.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:19:30.210 --> 00:19:32.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recogeremos provisiones y...</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:19:36.425 --> 00:19:37.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aquí estoy.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:19:37.467 --> 00:19:38.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reina Sarai.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:19:42.347 --> 00:19:43.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estabas en contra.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:19:43.682 --> 00:19:45.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y sigo en contra.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:46.018 --> 00:19:48.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero te apoyo de todos modos.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:49.062 --> 00:19:50.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gracias.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:50.355 --> 00:19:52.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fue un voto matrimonial, ¿no?</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:52.733 --> 00:19:56.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Mantenerte con vida</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cuando actúas como un idiota valiente?</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:59.823 --> 00:20:00.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vamos.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:20:06.079 --> 00:20:08.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Fuimos a la frontera</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>lo más rápido posible.</i></c.bg_transparent>

267
00:20:09.249 --> 00:20:11.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aventureros audaces de dos reinos</i></c.bg_transparent>

268
00:20:11.960 --> 00:20:13.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>cruzaron la brecha juntos,</i></c.bg_transparent>

269
00:20:14.046 --> 00:20:16.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>con la esperanza de ayudar a sus pueblos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

270
00:20:20.052 --> 00:20:24.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trueno, el rey de los Dragones,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>patrulla los cielos de sol a sol.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:20:24.431 --> 00:20:26.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entraremos a Xadia al atardecer</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:20:27.100 --> 00:20:31.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>y volveremos con el corazón del titán</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>antes del amanecer.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:20:31.772 --> 00:20:34.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Estas balistas podrán con el titán?</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:34.816 --> 00:20:39.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si apuntamos con precisión,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>daremos en el blanco y acabaremos.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:46.161 --> 00:20:47.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué pasa?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:20:48.247 --> 00:20:49.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nada.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:21:07.015 --> 00:21:10.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Salimos a la oscuridad</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>y pusimos manos a la obra.</i></c.bg_transparent>

278
00:21:37.337 --> 00:21:39.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vamos, la noche es breve.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:21:43.760 --> 00:21:46.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Con cada paso más cerca de Xadia,</i></c.bg_transparent>

280
00:21:46.555 --> 00:21:49.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>el corazón me latía más fuerte</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>por el miedo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

281
00:21:49.975 --> 00:21:53.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Este lugar albergaba</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>la promesa de nuestra salvación</i></c.bg_transparent>

282
00:21:53.729 --> 00:21:56.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>y la amenaza de nuestra destrucción.</i></c.bg_transparent>

283
00:22:05.949 --> 00:22:08.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Estábamos listos</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>para la pelea de nuestra vida.</i></c.bg_transparent>

284
00:22:14.207 --> 00:22:15.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Hallamos al titán,</i></c.bg_transparent>

285
00:22:16.126 --> 00:22:18.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>pero no era lo que esperábamos.</i></c.bg_transparent>

286
00:22:19.838 --> 00:22:22.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Está muerto. ¿Qué hacemos ahora?</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:22:22.924 --> 00:22:24.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te decepciones tanto.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:22:24.926 --> 00:22:27.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si está muerto, no hay que matarlo.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:22:27.179 --> 00:22:30.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debemos abrirlo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y llevarnos lo que necesitamos.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:22:57.334 --> 00:23:01.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tengo su carta desde hace unos días,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pero no me animo a abrirla.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:23:02.005 --> 00:23:03.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Parece una locura,</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:23:03.965 --> 00:23:07.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>pero, ahora, hay palabras que no me dijo.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:23:07.803 --> 00:23:09.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y están aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:23:09.721 --> 00:23:11.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esperan para cobrar vida.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:23:12.933 --> 00:23:14.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una vez que las lea...</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:23:15.644 --> 00:23:17.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando lea la última palabra,</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:23:18.438 --> 00:23:20.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>se habrá ido en serio.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:23:21.108 --> 00:23:22.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Para siempre.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:23:26.655 --> 00:23:28.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno. Gracias, Cebo.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:24:58.455 --> 00:25:00.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
